{"tid":1424732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"警察來了，我帶路！炸撚爆你哋。","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:37:09.000Z","uid":206916,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"56d86caa705dc778ff6d2fc0d341165f71a88cd2","tid":1424732,"uid":206916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"屌我老母，殺撚到埋身喇，呢一刻都仲可以咁撚港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班港豬老豆老母，你知唔知自己申請緊班狗去瘋狂抽插你仔女，抽插完之後仲要掟你十月懷胎、辛苦養大嘅骨肉去坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日左一句「暴徒」，右一句「淨係識得搞破壞、搞亂社會」，又喺度話又冇咗幾多舊磚、條電線俾人剪斷咗、畫花曬啲牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啫係你覺得一舊磚、一條電線、一幅牆係重要過班細路嘅命啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諷刺至極，搞撚笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至今時今日仲可以話：「你唔犯法，警察咪唔會拉你囉」、「行得正企得正你驚咩」、「警察點會無啦啦拉人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟我自己都進入咗平行時空，我一定係幻想出嚟，連港豬老豆老母潛意識都覺得「警察亂咁拉人」呢啲咁荒謬嘅嘢，由6月開始喺香港日日發生緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我在平行時空患上了被害妄想症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都係嗰句，粒Tear gas未掟到你咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 掟到你嘅話，我真心希望你可以Keep住可以好似宜家咁，講返同一番說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗要令你班豬清醒一下，或者令你哋收聲，唯有<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察來了我帶路，覺醒工作不能遲！一齊No gear enjoy tear gas 放題啦仆街</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b67e9d5f2ddcf5d365393af6c0585a8fb04aa0f","tid":1424732,"uid":206916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"深水埗手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}